metadata.name: LOS BLANCOS REMONTADAS 001
metadata.description:
REAL MADRID REMONTADA
Champions League 2021-2022 (STILL IMAGE)

This piece is dedicated for the 3 historical games for Real Madrid in the Champions League 2021-2022
Real Madrid battled back for three successive rounds against 3 big teams ( Paris saint-germain, Chelsea,Manchester City)
And now they are in the final for the 17th times looking for their 14th Champions League Trophy.

The piece shows some of the factors in those consecutive comebacks:
1. Real Madrid History
2. Karim Benzema (The Captin)
3. The Santiago Bernabeu
4. Carlo Ancelotti Super Subs
